{
  "texts": [
    "The role of law in this scenario is crucial.",
    "Technological inventions are not neutral, nor are they good per se.",
    "On the contrary, any new system embeds values, whether we like such an idea or not.",
    "106 Accordingly, lawyers and policymakers should take a hard look at the potentialities and risks of chatbots leveraging LLMs and create a regulatory and legal framework that is able to steer this technology towards the common good and a future in which humans are empowered rather than overwhelmed by it.",
    "Under the influence of the industry, part of the public debate about generative AI concentrated on the \"existential risk\" linked to this technology."
  ]
}